title: Key Ron and Rand Paul advisor acquitted in Iowa corruption trial
text: An Iowa jury has acquitted Jesse Benton, a longtime aide to both former congressman Ron Paul and Sen. Rand Paul (R-Ky.), on charges of lying to the FBI.
